2026-06-29 WIP
- Removed legacy yesmenn:* light ID/resource compatibility from L?YM while keeping shared YesMenn creative tab integration.
- Fixed slider-drag GUI dim by removing extra black overlay.
- Tint invisible spotlight marker with configured color and render it fullbright.
- Switched panel active plane to emissive model and added NeoForge fullbright data to panel/tube emitters.
- VILC test: reconstruct screen position from gl_FragCoord and disable first-person additive bubble pass.
- GUI dim also redraws number fields at drag opacity.
- Reverted vanilla/no-shader additive blend test because it overbrightened the scene.
- Center number input values in the light GUI during normal rendering.
- Wire colored light panel active plane to the fullbright model.
- VILC binds a dummy complete 3D texture for uBlockGrid when voxel shadows are unavailable to avoid GL_INVALID_OPERATION program texture usage.
- VILC vanilla pass now uses RenderTarget viewWidth/viewHeight for viewport and texcoord normalization.
- Add tint index to colored light panel fullbright plane.
- VILC disables and restores GL scissor state around the fullscreen light pass to rule out clipped quadrant artifacts.
- VILC samples depth with the actual depth texture size while keeping screen coordinates normalized to the visible view to avoid stale render-target quadrant reads.
